{"tid":1819702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「重開」如果伊朗件事係香港發生","createTime":"2020-01-11T04:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T05:30:05.000Z","uid":81236,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"565f40034bddc7ead219149e60e20c3e6ac6477a","tid":1819702,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:52:42.000Z","msg":"舊post唔好再推<br />\n侮辱左一班做錯敢認既伊朗軍人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗隻發言人可能會係咁回應<br />\n<br />\n部客機同啲乘客唔係果到出現就冇事<br />\n<br />\n部客機起飛係想去搶伊朗制空權<br />\n<br />\n係電光火石之間軍方㩒左個制<br />\n<br />\n係現場見唔到有攻擊性武器<br />\n<br />\nEr...要將個畫面拉闊啲黎睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有烏克蘭人製造左部客機帶一班加拿人去德黑蘭生事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以狗既標準<br />\n<br />\n咁簡單既大話都唔識講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無資格話自己係專業同埋受過訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff8ab22bbdc78239c31fafdedf833e7016507d3","tid":1819702,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:54:09.000Z","msg":"前個post我覺得對一班有錯敢認既人有啲唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本唔應該同班垃圾咁直接比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcab557e63bc48ef615304e8e61a05911b7e8498","tid":1819702,"uid":91432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:55:46.000Z","msg":"「親美烏克蘭人特登喺伊朗開航班，明係做架兩阻礙伊朗軍隊保家衛國！」<br />\n「啲加拿大籍伊朗人風頭火勢重要喺伊朗搭飛機，出事邊怪得人呀？」"},{"pid":"055065333a88b439f9270e94f4edcdb96a4d0ef4","tid":1819702,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:56:08.000Z","msg":"其他巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n架飛機同飛彈講 唔該借借 就可以"},{"pid":"e557ac1f02865ea88e89dd7c04d669a574f2d135","tid":1819702,"uid":2656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/yeloowww-07_CntGu_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fyeloowww-07_CntGu_1200x0.png&h=ba8c9754&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d61111a7966acd724266f1277faf3391ee19e98b","tid":1819702,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:57:41.000Z","msg":"唔好推之前個眼都突埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230e8cd191dd5cfd52cf132b402e0d2274c39f60","tid":1819702,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e557ac1f02865ea88e89dd7c04d669a574f2d135","tid":1819702,"uid":2656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/yeloowww-07_CntGu_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fyeloowww-07_CntGu_1200x0.png&h=ba8c9754&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:58:23.000Z","msg":"有巴打話係flying object<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ff6d6ad272bab9298ea8fc123d7e0018c688cf","tid":1819702,"uid":96648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:59:59.000Z","msg":"拉闊啲大波madam 對導彈嚟睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b56217c3c390be9247016be4bd08abd0741f6d3","tid":1819702,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T05:01:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我地只係係自己空域度演習，係架客機係<ins>電光火石</ins>之間闖入左我地演練範圍，其實<ins>只要佢地唔出現係相關空域就唔會有技術性安全問題</ins>，但佢地出現得係相關空域就會有相關風險。只要佢地係飛入相關演習空域前，<ins>講聲唔該借借就可以解決</ins>。相關責任及細節，乘客可以携同佢地嘅登機證，親身<ins>向現有機制技訴</ins>。我冇補充。</blockquote><br />\n搵人補埋<ins>最低武力</ins>"},{"pid":"c4d6e45f76ea0a751c42ed876a92117bb70e2021","tid":1819702,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T05:10:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2e9bc4828ee69b40da5614ed8d0a210c5dface02","tid":1819702,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T05:30:05.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}